 In this episode of #WithChude​, Peruzzi sits with Chude Jideonwo to shares details on his new album “Rum & Boogie“, the loss of his mum, meeting DMW record label owner Davido and more. “When I met David the only thing I knew was how to write songs.  I didn’t know any other thing but now I know the music business,” Peruzzi says, adding that’s it was when Davido posted his song on his Snapchat, “I didn’t know him before.” Watch the video below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 